  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "In a mixing bowl, combine shredded coconut, smoked paprika, sesame seeds, and garlic powder.",
    "Drizzle tahini sauce over the mixture until well combined. Add lime juice and mix thoroughly.",
    "Transfer the mixture onto a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Bake for 15 minutes or until golden brown and crispy."
